your spouse, that different dimension of their personality, perhaps something you don't have,

138
00:09:48,590 --> 00:09:55,770
was really attractive. Three years later, it drives you crazy, and it just gets worse,

139
00:09:56,970 --> 00:10:02,760
because you realize they're not going to change. As much as you wanted to change them,

140
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:10,340
they're not changing. They're getting rigid, and now you're stuck. I'm light with that,

141
00:10:10,340 --> 00:10:18,480
But reality is this, that personality issues, how God made us and hardwired us, can often be a deep struggle for marriages.

142
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:27,150
And after a few years, they don't want to appreciate the other and those gifts and that personality type.

143
00:10:30,090 --> 00:10:31,230
I'm more extroverted.

144
